{"tid":1110691,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【安心偷食】麥玲玲曾批馬明心穎關係將再進一步","createTime":"2019-04-16T15:48:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T19:08:25.000Z","uid":66271,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2302778aa455a496ca2bf6ad1ffd2e4bc3a13d8b","tid":1110691,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T15:48:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2019/4/1555395212_Sv-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2019%2F4%2F1555395212_Sv-1280w.jpg&h=1e9c747e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港著名堪輿學家麥玲玲師傅，去年底曾經為馬國明及黃心穎預測豬年愛情運，當中提到，馬明今年踏入合太歲年份，會有意結婚或訂婚，兩人的關係有機會再進一步。而馬明去年接受訪問時亦曾透露，早在2016年已買樓為娶老婆作好準備。今次爆出「安心偷食」事件，恐怕馬明難以如願了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/%E3%80%90%E5%AE%89%E5%BF%83%E5%81%B7%E9%A3%9F%E3%80%91%E9%BA%A5%E7%8E%B2%E7%8E%B2%E6%9B%BE%E6%89%B9%E9%A6%AC%E6%98%8E%E5%BF%83%E7%A9%8E%E9%97%9C%E4%BF%82%E5%B0%87%E5%86%8D%E9%80%B2%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5-169541\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%25BF%2583%25E5%2581%25B7%25E9%25A3%259F%25E3%2580%2591%25E9%25BA%25A5%25E7%258E%25B2%25E7%258E%25B2%25E6%259B%25BE%25E6%2589%25B9%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E6%2598%258E%25E5%25BF%2583%25E7%25A9%258E%25E9%2597%259C%25E4%25BF%2582%25E5%25B0%2587%25E5%2586%258D%25E9%2580%25B2%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%25AD%25A5-169541&d=gujWeq0O8VISlzAOvjwOFhPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=0cba5d03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/%E3%80%90%E5%AE%89%E5%BF%83%E5%81%B7%E9%A3%9F%E3%80%91%E9%BA%A5%E7%8E%B2%E7%8E%B2%E6%9B%BE%E6%89%B9%E9%A6%AC%E6%98%8E%E5%BF%83%E7%A9%8E%E9%97%9C%E4%BF%82%E5%B0%87%E5%86%8D%E9%80%B2%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5-169541</a>"},{"pid":"d36463fb243644bfdc6d7d614b58dd1ac1b85914","tid":1110691,"uid":66271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T15:51:0